Clarify,is,a,self,service,API,that,allows,developers,to,make,audio,and,video,files,actionable,via,search,extracted,keywords,and,topics,The,Clarify,API,provides,a,RESTful,API,to,extract,knowledge,from,audio,and,video,content,and,is,building,the,bridge,for,audio,and,video,to,become,just,as,searchable,as,textual,information